{"tid":2380433,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港開埠誌慶系列（一）】在那個後來叫維多利亞的海港上","createTime":"2021-01-26T01:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T16:47:28.000Z","uid":276716,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5cf230bfa96f5732ca3fea369a1cf639a0b725","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/01/blog-post_25.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhmssulphur.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fblog-post_25.html%3Fm%3D1&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=66dc668b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/01/blog-post_25.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\nFollow MeWe: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/scshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Fscshistory&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=ec9d73e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/scshistory</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><em>米字旗隨風飄揚，勘測船緩緩航行。船上的測量員忙於紀錄海岸線的形狀和距離。一個皮膚黝黑的男子，看起來是蜑家人，大概平時與英國人做買賣而學得幾句英語，此時正跟船上的翻譯半粵半英地交談，指著各處海灣海岬逐一道出名稱，讓旁邊的水手抄錄。而他們都沒有料到，這海港在半個世紀後會得到一個優雅的名字。</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港是南中國海最重要的貿易城市、金融中心和文化都會。適逢本年1月26日為香港開埠180周年，本部落格將推出一系列貼文，講述相關歷史。<br />\n<br />\n頭炮介紹一幅由英國人繪製，顯示香港在內的海圖。以下為截圖，文章最後連結可見完整版本。<br />\n<br />\n此圖為1778年出版，開埠63年前已清楚標示香港一帶島嶼。雖然地圖有明顯錯誤和扭曲，但其準確和辦識度已遠超任何一幅大清國繪畫的地圖。<br />\n<br />\n從英國繪製的地圖，可見很多熟悉地方。<br />\n<br />\nHe-Ong-Kong 香港<br />\n<br />\nCo-Long 九龍<br />\n<br />\nLammon 南丫島<br />\n<br />\nLantoe 大嶼山<br />\n<br />\nChang-Cheou 長洲<br />\n<br />\nChin-Falo 青衣/春花落<br />\n<br />\nPoo-Toy 蒲台島<br />\n<br />\nWag-Laang 橫欄島<br />\n<br />\n地圖中繪製得最為準確的一段，是沿東博寮海峽，經汲水門往屯門一帶，可能這就是商船常途經前往廣州的航線。香港島東部錯得較離譜，畫成分裂的兩個島嶼，據說是因為勘測船經過筲箕灣一帶時有濃霧遮蔽山嶺，令船員以為此處是一條海峽直通大潭灣。<br />\n<br />\n香港同時標上另一個名字，稱為「泛春洲（Fan-Chin-Cheou）」。此名並不見於其他文獻，不知出處為何。讀者如有線索請不吝賜教。<br />\n<br />\n新界東部有一條河流被標為「Iron River」，可能與馬鞍山鐵礦有關。<br />\n<br />\n歷史教科書將香港描述為荒島，但在開埠半個世紀之前，英國人已對香港的地理環境有不俗掌握，紀錄之準確也遠超大清國。毫無疑問，英國人此時已跟香港的原住民交往，「荒島」逐漸成為船隊補給、停泊之處，在這片大清國鞭長莫及的邊境地區進行各式「非法」的貿易活動。而此處的地利，和原住民的取態，將使南中國海北岸翻天覆地。"},{"pid":"2c3f13e149df0fb27c242f39bec09e996dbf438a","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47s8cV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47s8cV9.jpg&h=fda9a284&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f915f629db254f2890cd92fca1327b146c0dde","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxbtcWs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxbtcWs.jpg&h=5c5486ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3c4336b53ad8811ccee888ffab275b0e9e89a9b","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skK21Qa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskK21Qa.jpg&h=e524ba8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c70ba6b81f19060da6047c4803eb032d14b371b","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:23:16.000Z","msg":"參考<br />\n<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://nla.gov.au/nla.obj-230807888/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnla.gov.au%2Fnla.obj-230807888%2Fview&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=1ac00d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nla.gov.au/nla.obj-230807888/view</a><br />\n全幅地圖！<br />\n<br />\n2. <a href=\"https://hkjo.lib.hku.hk/archive/files/3eac0ef746c3c26cd345b58aabccb444.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkjo.lib.hku.hk%2Farchive%2Ffiles%2F3eac0ef746c3c26cd345b58aabccb444.pdf&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=cdc09eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkjo.lib.hku.hk/archive/files/3eac0ef746c3c26cd345b58aabccb444.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"1325bb8a80ada96ad7d9be351ef6a331bc3a1648","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKuKvKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKuKvKn.jpg&h=60b26416&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e35b5848bd9fc02136ad68836e0298f0eeb0ffd","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"Happy birthday to Hong Kong"},{"pid":"b6539eeeeb41dfe4b9c18ea6fda3bb0ee981b59e","tid":2380433,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"依篇幾好"},{"pid":"350e871f77405adfe252124c2e3e330192d1b779","tid":2380433,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f255da80958472b1c953018fbc189c62b1a947de","tid":2380433,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"528002e6bb70db51104282188ee55ea0eba4fd4c","tid":2380433,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:20:36.000Z","msg":"香港生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5804e473d7201d818b2e8c780f929322d314acd","tid":2380433,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcb4d078abf13061e30b4a8c046fdc7f2c752a30","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"},{"pid":"1f3cf75fd32d94e91f12f93e1807c7f8d8edf0d2","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"d22d751aa25b3dd43988d6196b48bed006ce7d6c","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a62555eaef34abcb8e5fde839414b568c55e46c","tid":2380433,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/mouse_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/mouse2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7800e76c143ee5ff7affdcb10b5bf7cfa2a8ecdc","tid":2380433,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"香港生日快樂"},{"pid":"c640d8ec7e0544a4a855f05afcea38d49ce8379e","tid":2380433,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"aab632d7f8591089b76ed567d5831834cf5baa00","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"ae009d2b135846d2949a10a33cadab87caedf113","tid":2380433,"uid":305674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"Happy birthday to Hong Kong"},{"pid":"9e01e3c5cf5ce0b1aeb257016219637e33770bc4","tid":2380433,"uid":305674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5cf230bfa96f5732ca3fea369a1cf639a0b725","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/01/blog-post_25.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhmssulphur.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fblog-post_25.html%3Fm%3D1&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=66dc668b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/01/blog-post_25.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\nFollow MeWe: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/scshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Fscshistory&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=ec9d73e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/scshistory</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><em>米字旗隨風飄揚，勘測船緩緩航行。船上的測量員忙於紀錄海岸線的形狀和距離。一個皮膚黝黑的男子，看起來是蜑家人，大概平時與英國人做買賣而學得幾句英語，此時正跟船上的翻譯半粵半英地交談，指著各處海灣海岬逐一道出名稱，讓旁邊的水手抄錄。而他們都沒有料到，這海港在半個世紀後會得到一個優雅的名字。</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港是南中國海最重要的貿易城市、金融中心和文化都會。適逢本年1月26日為香港開埠180周年，本部落格將推出一系列貼文，講述相關歷史。<br />\n<br />\n頭炮介紹一幅由英國人繪製，顯示香港在內的海圖。以下為截圖，文章最後連結可見完整版本。<br />\n<br />\n此圖為1778年出版，開埠63年前已清楚標示香港一帶島嶼。雖然地圖有明顯錯誤和扭曲，但其準確和辦識度已遠超任何一幅大清國繪畫的地圖。<br />\n<br />\n從英國繪製的地圖，可見很多熟悉地方。<br />\n<br />\nHe-Ong-Kong 香港<br />\n<br />\nCo-Long 九龍<br />\n<br />\nLammon 南丫島<br />\n<br />\nLantoe 大嶼山<br />\n<br />\nChang-Cheou 長洲<br />\n<br />\nChin-Falo 青衣/春花落<br />\n<br />\nPoo-Toy 蒲台島<br />\n<br />\nWag-Laang 橫欄島<br />\n<br />\n地圖中繪製得最為準確的一段，是沿東博寮海峽，經汲水門往屯門一帶，可能這就是商船常途經前往廣州的航線。香港島東部錯得較離譜，畫成分裂的兩個島嶼，據說是因為勘測船經過筲箕灣一帶時有濃霧遮蔽山嶺，令船員以為此處是一條海峽直通大潭灣。<br />\n<br />\n香港同時標上另一個名字，稱為「泛春洲（Fan-Chin-Cheou）」。此名並不見於其他文獻，不知出處為何。讀者如有線索請不吝賜教。<br />\n<br />\n新界東部有一條河流被標為「Iron River」，可能與馬鞍山鐵礦有關。<br />\n<br />\n歷史教科書將香港描述為荒島，但在開埠半個世紀之前，英國人已對香港的地理環境有不俗掌握，紀錄之準確也遠超大清國。毫無疑問，英國人此時已跟香港的原住民交往，「荒島」逐漸成為船隊補給、停泊之處，在這片大清國鞭長莫及的邊境地區進行各式「非法」的貿易活動。而此處的地利，和原住民的取態，將使南中國海北岸翻天覆地。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"原來為左同 blog 果邊一齊宣傳，已經冇左用廣東話入文一段時間。"},{"pid":"944b4d444084f4cd097613dc1f69292bb287e707","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e01e3c5cf5ce0b1aeb257016219637e33770bc4","tid":2380433,"uid":305674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5cf230bfa96f5732ca3fea369a1cf639a0b725","tid":2380433,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/01/blog-post_25.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhmssulphur.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fblog-post_25.html%3Fm%3D1&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=66dc668b\" dat